actions.name: Gale Wings
actions.description: Effect: If the user's HP is higher than 3/4 of their Max HP, all of the user's Flying-Type attacks gain [Priority 1], or have their [Priority X] increased by 1. This only works on attacks whose type is originally Flying-Type.
